s, has struggled for victories in recent months and is currently ranked 67th in the world.\", \"from\": 630, \"to\": 811, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The 36-year-old Briton\", \"from\": 630, \"to\": 652}, {\"ngram\": \"the only tennis player\", \"from\": 661, \"to\": 683}, {\"ngram\": \"two Olympic singles titles\", \"from\": 696, \"to\": 722}, {\"ngram\": \"victories\", \"from\": 742, \"to\": 751}, {\"ngram\": \"recent months\", \"from\": 755, \"to\": 768}, {\"ngram\": \"67th\", \"from\": 793, \"to\": 797}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 801, \"to\": 810}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Until a victory against Alexandre Muller in Doha earlier in February, he had been on a six-match losing streak and on Feb 28 admitted that he would probably not play on beyond the summer.\", \"from\": 813, \"to\": 1000, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 857, \"end\": 861, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Doha\", \"score\": 0.9999175471627533, \"rank\": 8.208787265641565e-05, \"text\": \"Doha\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Doha\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Doha\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a victory\", \"from\": 819, \"to\": 828}, {\"ngram\": \"Alexandre Muller\", \"from\": 837, \"to\": 853}, {\"ngram\": \"February\", \"from\": 873, \"to\": 881}, {\"ngram\": \"a six-match losing streak\", \"from\": 898, \"to\": 923}, {\"ngram\": \"Feb\", \"from\": 931, \"to\": 934}, {\"ngram\": \"the summer\", \"from\": 989, \"to\": 999}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cHopefully I can get the chance to compete at another one,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Murray, who has struggled following hip operations in recent years, told BBC Radio Four\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s Today programme, when asked if he would be present at the Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 1002, \"to\": 1231, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1066, \"end\": 1072, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2428946169265688e-32, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the chance\", \"from\": 1025, \"to\": 1035}, {\"ngram\": \"another one\", \"from\": 1050, \"to\": 1061}, {\"ngram\": \"hip operations\", \"from\": 1102, \"to\": 1116}, {\"ngram\": \"recent years\", \"from\": 1120, \"to\": 1132}, {\"ngram\": \"BBC Radio\", \"from\": 1139, \"to\": 1148}, {\"ngram\": \"Today programme\", \"from\": 1158, \"to\": 1173}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 1212, \"to\": 1230}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The three-time Grand Slam champion won singles golds at London 2012 and in Rio de Janeiro four years later, but could be in danger of missing out on qualification for the singles in Paris if his ranking continues to slide.\", \"from\": 1233, \"to\": 1455, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1289, \"end\": 1300, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tennis_at_the_2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9656200772706094, \"rank\": 0.03560398456178685, \"text\": \"London 2012\", \"types\": [\"Q500834\", \"Q1656682\", \"Q13219666\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tennis_at_the_2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tennis_at_the_2012_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1308, \"end\": 1322, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"score\": 0.9999999839942576, \"rank\": 1.6005628667093306e-08, \"text\": \"Rio de Janeiro\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\"}, {\"begin\": 1415, \"end\": 1420, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999953781753, \"rank\": 4.621763030304373e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org