gram\": \"the logical place\", \"from\": 1748, \"to\": 1765}, {\"ngram\": \"the curtain\", \"from\": 1783, \"to\": 1794}, {\"ngram\": \"his career\", \"from\": 1803, \"to\": 1813}, {\"ngram\": \"his three Slams\", \"from\": 1832, \"to\": 1847}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Scot enjoyed an encouraging victory over Canada\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s Denis Shapovalov at the Dubai Tennis Championships on Feb 25, but lost to France\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s Ugo Humbert on Feb 28.\", \"from\": 1856, \"to\": 2019, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1912, \"end\": 1917, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Denis_Thatcher\", \"score\": 0.9881246799540352, \"rank\": 0.0099153104711567, \"text\": \"Denis\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Denis_Thatcher\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Denis_Thatcher\"}, {\"begin\": 1997, \"end\": 2008, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ugo_Humbert\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ugo Humbert\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ugo_Humbert\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ugo_Humbert\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Scot\", \"from\": 1856, \"to\": 1864}, {\"ngram\": \"an encouraging victory\", \"from\": 1873, \"to\": 1895}, {\"ngram\": \"the Dubai Tennis Championships\", \"from\": 1932, \"to\": 1962}, {\"ngram\": \"Feb\", \"from\": 1966, \"to\": 1969}, {\"ngram\": \"Feb\", \"from\": 2012, \"to\": 2015}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After that defeat, Murray said: \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m likely not going to play past this summer.\", \"from\": 2021, \"to\": 2104, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2040, \"end\": 2046, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2428946169265688e-32, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that defeat\", \"from\": 2027, \"to\": 2038}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m\", \"from\": 2053, \"to\": 2061}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I get asked about it after every single match that I play, every single tournament that I play.\", \"from\": 2105, \"to\": 2200, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"every single match\", \"from\": 2132, \"to\": 2150}, {\"ngram\": \"every single tournament\", \"from\": 2164, \"to\": 2187}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m bored of the question, to be honest.\", \"from\": 2202, \"to\": 2247, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m\", \"from\": 2202, \"to\": 2210}, {\"ngram\": \"the question\", \"from\": 2220, \"to\": 2232}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m not going to talk more about that between now and whenever the time comes for me to stop.\", \"from\": 2248, \"to\": 2343, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m\", \"from\": 2248, \"to\": 2253}, {\"ngram\": \"the time\", \"from\": 2313, \"to\": 2321}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But yeah, I don\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t plan on playing much past this summer.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Murray, who has been playing with a metal hip since he underwent resurfacing surgery in 2019, also hopes he will be fit enough to compete at the French Open in May, which would be his first appearance at Roland Garros since 2020.REUTERS, AFP Men's tennis Andy Murray Olympics 2024 Retirement E-paper Newsletters Podcasts RSS Feed About Us Terms & Conditions Personal Data Protection Notice Need help?\", \"from\": 2344, \"to\": 2819, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2407, \"end\": 2413, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2428946169265688e-32, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q